\pf[1]This is a map of Sky Haven. I can still see where
I scribbled in my house, back when I was still a Jester.
Gallahad can duel wield weapons, so he can carry both weapons at the same time.
However, the weapon in his first slot will change his combos.
Wielding his \c[6]Training Sword\c[0] in the first slot gives him a combo called
\c[10]Vorporal Strike\c[0]! This combo is excellent for close range
But with his \c[6]Bag of Tricks\c[0] he can change his combo to the
\c[10]Vorporal Blast\c[0] which is great for long range \c[6]Magic Damage\c[0]
\pf[1]All the different tomes I had to study back
when I worked with the mages to hone my magic.
I still remember my first time conjuring a spark.
